BackBeam,is,a,full,stack,backend,platform,for,web,and,mobile,developers,Backbeam,provides,hosted,databases,push,notifications,a,real,time,API,personalized,emails,statistics,security,user,authentication,and,more,The,backbeam,REST,API,supports,JSON,and,JSONP,and,uses,a,custom,authorization,system,similar,to,OAuth,API,keys,are,required